#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:14
msgid ""
"Use the *Spin* tool to create the sort of objects that you would produce "
"on a lathe (this tool is often called a \"lathe\"-tool or a "
"\"sweep\"-tool in the literature, for this reason). In fact, it does a "
"sort of circular extrusion of your selected elements, centered on the 3D "
"cursor, and around the axis perpendicular to the working view..."
msgstr "使用 *旋绕* 工具来生成类似车床做出的结果。事实上，它生成选中元素的某种环状挤出，以3D游标为中心并且围绕着工作视图的垂直轴。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:20
msgid "The point of view will determine around which axis the extrusion spins..."
msgstr "观察点决定挤出将围绕哪个轴线进行旋绕。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:21
msgid "The position of the 3D cursor will be the center of the rotation."
msgstr "3D游标的位置将是旋绕的中心。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:23
msgid "Here are its settings:"
msgstr "以下是它的设置："

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:25
msgid "Steps"
msgstr "步数"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:26
msgid "Specifies how many copies will be extruded along the \"sweep\"."
msgstr "规定沿轴将有多少个复制体将被挤出。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:28
#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:92
msgid "Dupli"
msgstr "复制"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:28
msgid ""
"When enabled, will keep the original selected elements as separated "
"islands in the mesh (i.e. unlinked to the result of the spin extrusion)."
msgstr "选中时，原始结构与旋绕结果是分开的独立结构。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:30
#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:76
msgid "Angle"
msgstr "角度"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:31
msgid ""
"specifies the angle \"swept\" by this tool, in degrees (e.g. set it to "
"``180`` for half a turn)."
msgstr "规定旋绕的角度。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:32
msgid "Center"
msgstr "中心"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:33
msgid "Specifies the center of the spin. By default it uses the cursor position."
msgstr "规定旋绕的中心，默认使用3D游标位置。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:36
msgid "Axis"
msgstr "轴向"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:35
msgid "Specify the spin axis as a vector. By default it uses the view axis."
msgstr "规定旋绕轴向，默认使用当前视角轴向。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:39
msgid "Example"
msgstr "示例"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:44
msgid "Glass profile."
msgstr "玻璃轮廓"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:47
msgid ""
"First, create a mesh representing the profile of your object. If you are "
"modeling a hollow object, it is a good idea to thicken the outline. "
"(*Glass profile*) shows the profile for a wine glass we will model as a "
"demonstration."
msgstr "首先，创建出代表选中对象的网格。若你要塑造的是空心模型，最好给轮廓增加厚度。( *玻璃轮廓* )作为示范模型显示了一个酒杯的侧面轮廓"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:51
msgid ""
"Go to the *Edit* mode and select all the vertices of the Profile with "
":kbd:`A`."
msgstr "进入 *编辑* 模式，按下`A`全选轮廓的所有顶点。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:53
msgid ""
"We will be rotating the object around the cursor in the top view, so "
"switch to the top view with :kbd:`Numpad7`."
msgstr "我们将在顶视图围绕3D游标旋绕这个对象，因此按下`Numpad7`切换到顶视图。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:60
msgid "Glass profile, top view in Edit mode, just before spinning."
msgstr "玻璃场景，顶视图，编辑模式，刚要进行旋绕之前。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:63
msgid ""
"Place the cursor along the center of the profile by selecting one of the "
"vertices along the center, and snapping the 3D cursor to that location "
"with :menuselection:`Mesh --> Cursor --> Selection`. (*Glass profile, top"
" view in* *Edit* *mode, just before spinning*) shows the wine glass "
"profile from top view, with the cursor correctly positioned."
msgstr ""
"要在场景中心放置3D游标，可以沿中心选择一个顶点再将3D游标吸附到选中点的位置，通过菜单选择：网格 → 游标→选中项。（ "
"*玻璃场景，顶视图，编辑模式，刚要进行旋绕之前* )显示了从顶视图看到的玻璃酒杯轮廓，且游标被正确的放置。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:69
msgid ""
"Click the *Spin* button. If you have more than one 3D view open, the "
"cursor will change to an arrow with a question mark and you will have to "
"click in the window containing the top view before continuing. If you "
"have only one 3D view open, the spin will happen immediately. (*Spun "
"profile*) shows the result of a successful spin."
msgstr ""
"点击 *旋绕* "
"按钮。若你有不只1个3D视图打开，光标将变成带问号的箭头，你只需要在顶视图窗口上点击下。若你只有1个3D视图打开，旋绕操作将立即进行。( "
"*旋转剖面* ) 显示了一次成功的旋绕结果。"

