#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:108
msgid "Merge Duplicates"
msgstr "合并重叠点"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:113
msgid "Duplicate vertices"
msgstr "重叠点"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:116
msgid ""
"The spin operation leaves duplicate vertices along the profile. You can "
"select all vertices at the seam with Box select (:kbd:`B`) shown in "
"(*Seam vertex selection*) and perform a *Remove Doubles* operation."
msgstr "旋绕操作会留下重叠点。你可以用框选(快捷键`B`)来选择接缝处的所有顶点，然后执行 *移除重叠点* 操作。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:121
msgid ""
"Notice the selected vertex count before and after the *Remove Doubles* "
"operation (*Vertex count after removing doubles*). If all goes well, the "
"final vertex count (38 in this example) should match the number of the "
"original profile noted in (*Mesh data - Vertex and face numbers*). If "
"not, some vertices were missed and you will need to weld them manually. "
"Or, worse, too many vertices will have been merged."
msgstr ""
"注意选中顶点在 *移除重叠点* 前后的数目。若一切顺利，最终顶点数（本例中为38）应该匹配原始轮廓的数量，数据显示在（ *网格数据 - "
"顶点和面数* ）。若不是这样，某些顶点被遗漏了，你需要手动焊接它们。或者更糟糕，太多的顶点需要被合并。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:129
msgid "Merging two vertices in one"
msgstr "合并两个顶点为一个"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:131
msgid ""
"To merge (weld) two vertices together, select both of them by :kbd"
":`Shift-RMB` clicking on them. Press :kbd:`S` to start scaling and hold "
"down :kbd:`Ctrl` while scaling to scale the points down to 0 units in the"
" X, Y and Z axis. :kbd:`LMB` to complete the scaling operation and click "
"the *Remove Doubles* button in the *Buttons* window, *Editing* context "
"(also available with :menuselection:`[W] --> Remove Doubles`)."
msgstr ""
"要把两个顶点合并到一起，`Shift-右键`点击它们来同时选择两个。按下`S` "
"开始缩放并在缩放时按住`Ctrl`来在X，Y，Z坐标都缩放到0。`鼠标左键`点击完成缩放操作，并点击侧栏中的 *移除重叠点* 按钮（也可以通过按下"
" `W` → 移除重叠点）。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:138
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can use :menuselection:`[W] --> Merge` from the same "
"*Specials* menu (or :kbd:`Alt-M`). Then, in the new pop-up menu, choose "
"whether the merged vertex will be at the center of the selected vertices "
"or at the 3D cursor. The first choice is better in our case!"
msgstr ""
"另外，你可以通过按下`W`→合并，在相同的 *特殊* 菜单中 "
"（或快捷键`Alt-M`）。然后，在新弹出的菜单中，选择合并的顶点将在选择点的中心或在3D游标处。在这里最好选第一个选项。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:145
msgid "Recalculate Normals"
msgstr "重新计算法线"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:147
msgid ""
"All that remains now is to recalculate the normals to the outside by "
"selecting all vertices, pressing :kbd:`Ctrl-N` and validating *Recalc "
"Normals Outside* in the pop-up menu."
msgstr "现在就只剩下重新计算法线到外侧，通过全选所有顶点，按下`Ctrl-N`，然后确认弹出菜单中的 *法线朝向* 为向外。"

